Sorry for inconvenience with my project and let me investigate about this.

By the way this repository,
https://github.com/miyosuda/TensorFlowAndroidDemo
is using .a library files and headers from TensorFlow 0.6.0.

I've recently upgraded another repository with MNIST sample
https://github.com/miyosuda/TensorFlowAndroidMNIST
with latest TensorFlow r0.8.

Let me upgrade TensorFlowAndroidDemo with r0.8 too.
